{"tid":1965953,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［cls種族歧視］論racist，點夠共產黨玩，一齊黎睇下中國係點歧視外國人","createTime":"2020-04-09T21:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T23:49:48.000Z","uid":116560,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"79821352df688e0afbabb1adb1e8d8b891396101","tid":1965953,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:13:23.000Z","msg":"source<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=149596133203660&amp;id=104162294413711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D149596133203660%26id%3D104162294413711&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=23db4ad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=149596133203660&amp;id=104162294413711</a><br />\n<br />\n望到都覺得cls，類比就好似美國餐廳同商店只係比白人入咁，無任何一個2020年既文明國家容許咁既事<br />\n有d外國人甚至可能買唔到食物<br />\n中國先係最種族歧視既國家，今日開始學用呢個tag<br />\n#CCPIsRacist<br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n共匪政權帶領帶頭行種族歧視政策<br />\n#呢d先係Racist<br />\n未知世衛同譚得塞出聲未<br />\n<br />\n中國統治下既餐廳、食肆、店鋪，絕大多數禁止外國人入來，不論你是否入籍中國，只要係非華人面孔就免進。<br />\n<br />\n片段a.中國一間賣防疫用品既店禁止外國人入內<br />\n拍攝片段既非裔男子、同埋其他係門口既俄羅斯人都無法入內購買防疫物資。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245780546375929856?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245780546375929856%3Fs%3D19&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=74d8ee94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245780546375929856%3Fs%3D19&h=e430e351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245780546375929856?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n片段b.一名非中國籍男子在商場門口問保安：「我不能內進嗎？」<br />\n保安回答：「領導說外國人不能內進。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245780589199806464?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245780589199806464%3Fs%3D09&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=4ba6cb42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245780589199806464%3Fs%3D09&h=3eb17b68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245780589199806464?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n片段c.一名非中國籍女子，因為她不是中國人，在不能進入餐廳，被迫隔著玻璃看著家人用餐，透過丈夫遞食物，在室外的小凳上進食。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245781664040509440?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245781664040509440%3Fs%3D19&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=7919c97b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245781664040509440%3Fs%3D19&h=309db59f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245781664040509440?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n片段d.眾所鳩知而家中國用健康碼黎判斷一個人有幾多公民權利，而呢一名非裔男子即使有綠色健康碼，亦無法進入超級市場，理由僅僅是他為外國人。而佢亦提到「外國人吃甚麼？」意即外國人在中國買食物非常困難。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245787153470119937?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245787153470119937%3Fs%3D09&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=ee282f07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245787153470119937%3Fs%3D09&h=8b2f4da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245787153470119937?s=09</a>"},{"pid":"7ab79e4e1ff2184e451ceaa8f8556c28daa2279f","tid":1965953,"uid":116560,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:19:38.000Z","msg":"同場加映 #CCPisRacist<br />\n班中國山番根本反人類<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/10/051845_3404d28159c27e4bcf0a1f2f60088e91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F10%2F051845_3404d28159c27e4bcf0a1f2f60088e91.jpg&h=97b50980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hBeXxtK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhBeXxtK.jpg&h=7941af50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bd8eeb60729d5d4c196cb33fa0044c0eb71b85d","tid":1965953,"uid":116560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歧視大國學人扮慘，投訴人歧視佢"},{"pid":"547ed94d5f52fe6984bc7c1b03b9a7dfc00a764e","tid":1965953,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:35:36.000Z","msg":"講咁多做咩? 中共殺咗幾多人，開咗幾多集中營?"},{"pid":"0566e47611d78841e77cd9c57f89631c68e7e365","tid":1965953,"uid":267423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWQ4cz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWQ4cz8.jpg&h=9d7db78d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eae6e0b39dd243730cccab1038d31527a5e629b","tid":1965953,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:40:27.000Z","msg":"呢位係混血兒model<br />\n就因為係混血，微博下面都係有好多痴線評論的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wtydQnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwtydQnB.jpg&h=50709740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuttEfY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuttEfY.jpg&h=ed1d5a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwh2JHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqwh2JHC.jpg&h=f0c18764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvuTQnw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvuTQnw.jpg&h=310fbd22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNXKcAT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNXKcAT.jpg&h=15f17dd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"p