%3Fs%3D09&h=3eb17b68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245780589199806464?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n片段c.一名非中國籍女子，因為她不是中國人，在不能進入餐廳，被迫隔著玻璃看著家人用餐，透過丈夫遞食物，在室外的小凳上進食。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245781664040509440?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245781664040509440%3Fs%3D19&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=7919c97b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245781664040509440%3Fs%3D19&h=309db59f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245781664040509440?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n片段d.眾所鳩知而家中國用健康碼黎判斷一個人有幾多公民權利，而呢一名非裔男子即使有綠色健康碼，亦無法進入超級市場，理由僅僅是他為外國人。而佢亦提到「外國人吃甚麼？」意即外國人在中國買食物非常困難。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245787153470119937?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245787153470119937%3Fs%3D09&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=ee282f07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTruthAbtChina%2Fstatus%2F1245787153470119937%3Fs%3D09&h=8b2f4da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TruthAbtChina/status/1245787153470119937?s=09</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dNpWWFw-3Jo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdNpWWFw-3Jo&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=0ee4df0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dNpWWFw-3Jo</a>"},{"pid":"2a78f3bc02e8c6b38fb60683ea248947e7bf7ac7","tid":1965953,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:51:57.000Z","msg":"13% of population, 50% of crimes"},{"pid":"5a4c664df75d8c8ced1b7ae72fb37f675f8bf201","tid":1965953,"uid":24730,"like":0,"disli